{"tid":2515733,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"菲律賓為稱中國為「戇鳩死毒撚」致歉 改稱「武漢肺炎大恩人」","createTime":"2021-05-04T07:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T07:42:55.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c6464326f5d53823120331a8f14e0d15d7e3685b","tid":2515733,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:38:16.000Z","msg":"菲國外長就發表帶粗口帖文道歉 總統稱中國是恩人<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓外長洛欽就他在社交網站發表帶有粗口的帖文，要求中國船隻離開兩國有主權爭議水域，向中方道歉。<br />\n<br />\n總統府發言人說，洛欽已經向中國大使致歉，又引述洛欽表示，發表有關言論是因為有些事惹怒了他。<br />\n<br />\n總統杜特爾特強調，中國仍然是菲律賓的恩人，雖然菲律賓與中國之間發生衝突，但並不意味菲方要變得無禮，不尊重別人，菲律賓事實上亦有太多事要感謝中國，無論是過去的幫助，或者是現在的協助。<br />\n<br />\n杜特爾特昨日接種中國國藥集團的新冠疫苗，他在接種後表示感覺不錯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589150-20210504.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589150-20210504.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnjYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=36636aba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589150-20210504.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=261bb5ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589150-20210504.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6c3af2a028bcc905ce46fa3729ab966c4df148a5","tid":2515733,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:40:45.000Z","msg":"杜特爾特正契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7dda40f97c40dc66a04c494b127d8da23898b9","tid":2515733,"uid":371175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:42:55.000Z","msg":"識玩 彈出彈入 撚完人之後道個歉 吹佢唔脹"}]}